'''''Sprinter''''' ni firime yimikino ya 2018 izenguruka umukinnyi unyura mubibazo byumuryango, iyobowe na Storm Saulter. Will Smith na Jada Pinkett Smith bari abaproducer bayobora uyu musaruro. <ref>https://www.theguardian.com/film/2019/sep/05/sprinter-review-jamaica-athletics-drama</ref> <ref>https://www.indiewire.com/2019/05/storm-saulter-sprinter-will-jada-smith-overbrook-1202131740/</ref> Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere muIserukiramuco rya Filime y'Abanyamerika muri 2018 aho yatsindiye ibihembo bya Best Narrative Feature, Igihembo cyabaterankunga mu cyiciro cya Filime Nziza n’Umuyobozi mwiza. <ref>https://medium.com/@writerjudy7/storm-saulters-sprinter-takes-home-top-award-at-american-black-film-festival-90572d0acd74</ref>

== Icegeranyo ==
Umwangavu wo muri Jamayike uremerewe na se udahungabana na musaza we udahungabana yizera ko izamuka rya meteorike mu isiganwa ry’imirima rishobora kumuhuza na nyina, wabaga muri Amerika mu buryo butemewe n'amategeko mu myaka icumi ishize. <ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sprinter</ref>

